### Key Files to Know
- src/lib/sharedHTMLTemplate.ts - HTML/CSS template (shared by frontend & server)
- server/src/utils/pdfGenerator.ts - Playwright PDF generation logic
- server/src/middleware/auth.ts - JWT validation & admin enforcement
- supabase/functions/.../index.ts - Edge Function proxy

### For Updates
Always maintain compatibility between:
1. Frontend PDF download logic (src/utils/generateFullRecordPDF.ts)
2. Shared HTML template (src/lib/sharedHTMLTemplate.ts)
3. Server HTML generator (server/src/utils/htmlGenerator.ts)
4. CSS styling for print/PDF rendering
